  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n\r\n*Summary*: `Reset to default` and `Done` buttons overlap `Amount` and `Total Fee`\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nA keyboard should not overlap wallet screen details, screen should be adjusted dynamically\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/39310438-09d56682-4973-11e8-8c74-71c2707a58da.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- /faucet some funds\r\n- Tap wallet\r\n- Tap specify amount and enter some valid amount\r\n- Tap advanced\r\n- Tap into transaction fee\r\n- Tap into gas limit or gas price\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop\r\n* Operating System: Android 7.0 Huawei P10 lite 5.2\"",
